item.title: Getting Intentional, with Chris Bailey
item.description: Chris Bailey is back to talk about his new book, The Intention Stack, fundamental human values, and why S.M.A.R.T. goals aren't very smart. Feed: https://www.relay.fm/focused/feed

item.title: Daniel and Alison (Darnell Quintz and Bids for Analysis)
item.description:
Daniel and I are talking about an insulting auction house lady, the four horsemen of our marriage, the feeling I get when he talks about politics with me and the feeling he gets when he sees the feeling I get, painting over the Netflix sticker on his book, my dang thumbs, parenting a child who is autistic and so much more.
